    "section_UEXTzq": {
      "type": "section",
      "blocks": {
        "text_kfwf4J": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "t:names.text",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Better Playmats. Faster Turnaround. Zero Friction.<\/p><p>Your Vision. Our Neoprene. Finally, a production partner that speaks \"Tabletop\" and delivers high-fidelity custom playmats with transparent pricing you can actually plan around.<\/p><p><strong>[Button: Get a Transparent Quote]<\/strong><\/p><p><strong>[The Partnership Section]<\/strong><\/p><p>We Manage the Production. You Make the Game Legendary.<\/p><p>As a creator, you shouldn't have to be a supply chain expert to get a premium product. We’ve streamlined the neoprene process—from sourcing raw materials to final shipping—so you can focus on your backers and your mechanics.<\/p><p><strong>[The Features Grid]<\/strong><\/p><p>Why Crowdfunding Creators Choose Us:<\/p><ul><li><strong>Gallery-Quality 1200 DPI Printing<\/strong><br\/>Your art shouldn’t be a compromise. Our ultra-high-resolution printing ensures every hex, card slot, and character detail is crisp, vibrant, and exactly as you designed it.<\/li><li><strong>Stitched or Unstitched—Your Choice<\/strong><br\/>We offer the industry-standard sizes your players expect, with premium stitched edges for durability or clean unstitched cuts for a sleek, edge-to-edge look.<\/li><li><strong>Scale That Fits Your Success<\/strong><br\/>Whether you’re a boutique indie needing a <strong>low MOQ<\/strong> or a breakout hit requiring thousands of units, our production line scales with your campaign’s momentum.<\/li><li><strong>A \"No-Guesswork\" Timeline<\/strong><br\/>We give you realistic production windows based on real-world logistics. No \"crowdfunding fluff\"—just honest dates that help you keep your \"Updates\" tab positive.<\/li><\/ul>",
            "width": "fit-content",
            "max_width": "none",
            "alignment": "left",
            "type_preset": "custom",
            "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
            "font_size": "1rem",
            "line_height": "normal",
            "letter_spacing": "normal",
            "case": "none",
            "wrap": "pretty",
            "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
            "background": false,
            "background_color": "#00000026",
