            "content": "<p><strong>We Manage the Production. You Make the Game Legendary.<\/strong><\/p><p>Your Vision. Our Process. Finally, a production partner that speaks \"Tabletop\" and delivers high-fidelity custom playmats with transparent pricing you can actually plan around.<\/p><p>As a creator, you shouldn't have to be a supply chain expert to get a premium product. We’ve streamlined the neoprene process—from sourcing raw materials to final shipping—so you can focus on your backers and your mechanics.<\/p>",
